data.description: Welcome to this upgraded duplex in W. Lancaster, where each unit has two bedrooms and one bathroom for comfortable living. The exterior showcases modern siding and upgraded windows, enhancing both aesthetics and energy efficiency. Inside, unit one- features elegant tile floors and new countertops, creating a fresh and stylish atmosphere. Meanwhile, Unit 2 is tenant-occupied, adding a sense of security to this well-maintained property. Whether you're an off-site investor or planning to live in half and rent the other, this duplex offers a blend of modern upgrades and is in a convenient Lancaster location- near freway and shopping!
